<h3>Sizes</h3>
<p>The default size uses 36pt for the number and 40px for an icon.</p>
{% call components.example(palette='light') %}
    <div class="centered">
        <rh-stat icon="rh-telecom-vertical">
            <span slot="statistic">80%</span>
            <span slot="description">of Fortune Global 500 telecom companies<sup>1</sup></span>
        </rh-stat>
    </div>
{%- endcall %}
<p>A large stat uses 48pt for the number and 64px for an icon.</p>
{% call components.example(palette='light') %}
    <div class="centered">
        <rh-stat size="large" icon="rh-telecom-vertical">
            <span slot="statistic">80%</span>
            <span slot="description">of Fortune Global 500 telecom companies<sup>1</sup></span>
        </rh-stat>
    </div>
{%- endcall %}
<p>Both size variations use 18pt for body text and 20pt for titles.</p>

<h3>Configurations/variants</h3>
<p>An icon can be added as the first element in a statistic.</p>
<pfe-cta>
    <a href="/get-started/icon-library/">Learn more about using icons</a> 
</pfe-cta> <!------------------ADD MARGIN BELOW CTA------------------>
{% call components.example(palette='light') %}
    <div class="centered">
        <rh-stat icon="rh-telecom-vertical">
            <span slot="statistic">80%</span>
            <span slot="description">of Fortune Global 500 telecom companies<sup>1</sup></span>
        </rh-stat>
    </div>
{%- endcall %}
<p>A call to action can be added as the last element in a statistic.</p>
{% call components.example(palette='light') %}
    <div class="centered">
        <rh-stat icon="rh-telecom-vertical">
            <span slot="statistic">80%</span>
            <span slot="description">of Fortune Global 500 telecom companies<sup>1</sup></span>
            <pfe-cta slot="cta">
                <a href="#">Learn more</a>
            </pfe-cta>
        </rh-stat>
    </div>
{%- endcall %}
<p>A stat can be placed inside a card.</p>
{% call components.example(palette='light') %}
    <div class="centered">
        <img src="{{ '/assets/statistic/stat-config-in-card.svg' | url }}" alt="Example of a stat centered in a card"
            style="--inline-img-max-width: 406px;">
    </div>
{%- endcall %}

<h3>Layout</h3>
<p>All content in a stat should use the same alignment. Currently all stat content is centered.</p>
{% call components.example(palette='light') %}
    <div class="centered">
        <rh-stat>
            <span slot="title">More than</span>
            <span slot="statistic">90%</span>
            <span slot="description">of Fortune 500 companies rely on Red Hat.<sup>1</sup></span>
        </rh-stat>
    </div>
{%- endcall %}

{%- endcall %}

